definitions.definition: A certain way of speaking , of using words; especially that associated with a particular job or interest .
Of a word, the quality of being lexicalized ; especially as jargon or slang .

main_definition: A certain way of speaking , of using words; especially that associated with a particular job or interest .
secondary_definitions: Of a word, the quality of being lexicalized ; especially as jargon or slang .
( archaic , rare ) Speech, discussion or debate .
